  }							      	}							      }								  
  while ( ! stringstack . isEmpty ( ) ) {		      	while ( ! stringstack . empty ( ) ) {			      while ( ! stringstack . empty ( ) ) {			  
    result = stringstack . peek ( ) + result ;		      	  result = stringstack . top ( ) + result ;		    	result = stringstack . top ( ) + result ;
